#==============================================================================#
  X11::Terminal
#==============================================================================#

A module to provide an object-oriented interface to launching X terminal
windows.

#==============================================================================#

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

#==============================================================================#

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires at least perl 5.6.0 and these other modules and libraries:

  Moose

